reviewText: I purchased this for my granddaughter for Halloween, and she really likes Dora the Explorer.  She liked the movie and watches it often.

My granddaughter and grandson LOVE. Dora.....this does not disappoint, I have never purchased a Dora item from Amazon that did not please the munchkins......A wide selection is available, delivery is prompt and the little ones are thrilled.  What more could a grandmother ask for?
This was a great DVD for my little guy - he loves Dora!  It's nice to have all the Halloween episodes on one disc.
Baby Johnny loves his explorer girlfriend
Fun with Dora, Boots and friends. Another Dora treasure.

My 3-year-old Japanese daughter truely LOVES Dora. She has been watching Dora every day. As an English learner whose mother language is Japanese, I am watching Dora with her and found Dora movie really helpful to learn English. Happy Halloween!!

DVD came quickly  and was packaged great.  It was a cute little dvd that my 2 year old grandaughter really
enjoyed.
Got this dvd quickly and have watched it alot!!
My 3 year old LOVES this. She loves the Halloween episodes the best.
My toddler loves this Halloween themed DVD. I wanted some fun, wholesome Halloween viewing for her. Top it off with typical Dora learning skills, and we are very happy with the purchase.
This cartoon is perfect for your little ones that love Dora. It's great for Halloween I would recommend this product.
